| Problem                                      | Solution                                                                                                                                                      |
|----------------------------------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| Charging does not start (battery charger).   | - Insert the battery.                                                                                                                                         |
|                                              | - Reinsert the battery in the correct orientation.                                                                                                            |
|                                              | - Make sure that the charger is correctly plugged in.                                                                                                         |
|                                              | - Ensure that the plug adapter is correctly connected to the charger.                                                                                         |
| Charging is slow.                            | Charge the battery at room temperature.                                                                                                                       |
| The indicator lamp blinks, but the battery   | - **There is dirt on the battery terminals:** Clean the terminals with a soft, dry cloth (ðŸ“– 30).                                                              |
| does not charge.                             | - **The battery has been charged many times:** The battery has reached the end of its charging life. Purchase a new battery. If the battery still fails to charge, contact your Fujifilm dealer (ðŸ“– 298). |
| The power supply icon is not displayed.      | Confirm that **ON** is selected for **USB POWER SUPPLY SETTING** (ðŸ“– 241).                                                                                    |
